reviews.text:
I think that this place is quite good but the road is narrow and a lot of car parked nearby the street.
Although I give 3 stars but I also recommend you to go.

Ching Chung Koon is a Taoist temple established in 1960, but the current complex was first built in 1960 followed by extensive renovation and expansion. The name Ching Chung is based the metaphor likened a righteous person to an evergreen pine tree. As the major base of the Dragon Gate sect of the Quanzhen school of Taoism in Hongkong, it is a must visit place to those who are interested in Taoism, traditional Chinese buildings, Chinese calligraphy and vegetarian dishes. It can be easily reached by taking Light Rail 506 at the MTR Siu Hong Station.

In the this day, In Ching Chung Koon for  lunch.
 We're eating the vegetables food. This dish has a good taste and boiled.👍😋
Peace & beautiful scene,  go for weekday, free of charge
good for every one enjoyed so much

result.name: 青松觀

reviews.text: 地潔人靈😍😍
青松觀是屯門地標之一  其餘兩個 佛教 妙法寺 青山禪院 60年代 70年代製衣廠蓬勃嘅時候 老闆 包車旅遊 食素的地方 現今的青松觀 保持完好 尤其是 地標之一  盆景 運往香港 展覽 現金交通十分方便 有輕鐵公共巴士直達 是值得遊覽嘅地方 環境清靜 三清大殿 假山 水池 是 地標之一 I
歷史悠久的道觀，環境優美，但因時代變遷，週邊被醫院(屯門醫院)及其他建築物包圍，令人容易錯過一個好去處！
環境唔錯，有不少的樹仔頭睇。

reviews.text: Vast selection of baby related merchandise, Parents favorite. A huge supermarket sits next to this department store as well. A true one stop shop for families
Huge mall, connected to other shopping as well.  Good transportation options in and out.
Great place for shopping, especially for beauty products! Family mall with everything you need.

Central location. Linked to 5 or 6 other shopping arcades. Linked to the subway line at Tuen Mun station. Many car parks, and some offer free parking with purchase. I'm happy with this place as I'm always able to find whatever I'm looking for here. Finding my car after getting parking ticket stamped is always a challenge tho.
This is the closest to home and what you get.ftom.anywhere, you get it here  mostly, why ho anywhere else. My kids are practical, when they are here, they love it just here.
